prompt: What’s our conversion rate from lead to opportunity to closed-won?
sql_query: WITH lead_counts AS ( SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT TRANSACTION_ID) AS TOTAL_LEADS, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN REVENUE_STAGE = 'Opportunity' THEN TRANSACTION_ID END) AS TOTAL_OPPORTUNITIES, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN REVENUE_STAGE = 'Closed Won' THEN TRANSACTION_ID END) AS TOTAL_CLOSED_WON FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_KPI6_SHIPMENT_REVENUE_BY_SALESPERSON ) SELECT TOTAL_LEADS, TOTAL_OPPORTUNITIES, TOTAL_CLOSED_WON, CAST(TOTAL_OPPORTUNITIES AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(TOTAL_LEADS, 0) * 100 AS LEAD_TO_OPPORTUNITY_RATE, CAST(TOTAL_CLOSED_WON AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(TOTAL_OPPORTUNITIES, 0) * 100 AS OPPORTUNITY_TO_CLOSED_RATE, CAST(TOTAL_CLOSED_WON AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(TOTAL_LEADS, 0) * 100 AS OVERALL_CONVERSION_RATE FROM lead_counts LIMIT 100

prompt: Which accounts have the highest open pipeline and no recent activity?
sql_query: WITH LastActivity AS ( SELECT SALES_REP, MAX(TRANSACTION_DATE) AS LAST_TRANSACTION_DATE FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_KPI1_SALES_LEADER_BOARD GROUP BY SALES_REP ), Pipeline AS ( SELECT s.SALES_REP, SUM(CAST(s.OPEN_ORDER_REVENUE AS NUMERIC)) AS TOTAL_OPEN_PIPELINE, COUNT(DISTINCT s.CUSTOMER_NAME__C) AS UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS, l.LAST_TRANSACTION_DATE, DATEDIFF('day', l.LAST_TRANSACTION_DATE, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()) AS DAYS_SINCE_LAST_ACTIVITY FROM PENGUIN_INTELLIGENCE_HUB.GOLD.VW_KPI2_SALES_PERFORMANCE_RANKING s JOIN LastActivity l ON s.SALES_REP = l.SALES_REP GROUP BY s.SALES_REP, l.LAST_TRANSACTION_DATE HAVING DAYS_SINCE_LAST_ACTIVITY > 30 ORDER BY TOTAL_OPEN_PIPELINE DESC LIMIT 100 ) SELECT * FROM LASTACTIVITY
